@startuml sd_SalaryCalculationService_calculateAll
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title SalaryCalculationService.calculateAll(yearMonth, trialRun, username) - 批量工资计算

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryCalculation\nService" as CalcSvc
participant "EmployeeRepository" as EmpRepo
participant "UserRepository" as UsrRepo
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as ItemRepo
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo
participant "TaxService" as TaxSvc
participant "SocialSecurity\nService" as SsSvc

Client -> CalcSvc: calculateAll("202403", false, "admin")
note right of CalcSvc : @Transactional
CalcSvc -> EmpRepo: findByActiveTrue()
EmpRepo --> CalcSvc: List<Employee> (全部在职员工)
CalcSvc -> UsrRepo: findByUsername("admin")
UsrRepo --> CalcSvc: User (操作人)
CalcSvc -> ItemRepo: findByActiveTrueOrderBySortOrder()
ItemRepo --> CalcSvc: List<SalaryItem> (14个工资项)
note right of CalcSvc : 获取上月记录用于累计值

loop 每个在职员工
  CalcSvc -> CalcSvc: calculateSingle(emp, ym, items, null)
  note right #F0F8FF
    **内部顺序:**
    1. 计算各工资项值
    2. 计算社保公积金(SsSvc)
    3. 计算个税(TaxSvc)
    4. 计算实发合计
    5. 构建SalaryRecord
  end note
  CalcSvc -> RecRepo: save(record)
  RecRepo --> CalcSvc: 持久化SalaryRecord
end
note right of CalcSvc : trialRun=false → status=CONFIRMED\ntrialRun=true → status=DRAFT
CalcSvc --> Client: List<SalaryRecord>
note right of Client : 返回本批次全部工资记录
@enduml
